        "new_string": "# Ralph Progress Log\nStarted: Wed Apr  1 15:14:08 CEST 2026\n---\n\n## Story #39: Project Collaboration — 2026-04-01\n\n### What was built\nFull project collaboration feature: sharing personal projects via Supabase, invite links, real-time sync, member management, notifications, and task assignment.\n\n### Architecture decisions\n- **SyncService in renderer**: Since the authenticated Supabase client lives in the renderer process, all Supabase interactions (write-through, Realtime subscriptions, invite management) are handled there. SQLite operations stay in main via IPC.\n- **Hybrid sync model**: Personal projects stay local-only. Shared projects write-through to both SQLite and Supabase Postgres. Offline edits queue locally in `sync_queue` table.\n- **Labels sync by name**: Labels are personal (each user has own colors). Only label names are synced via `label_names` JSON array on shared_tasks. Missing labels are auto-created locally.\n- **Supabase RLS**: All shared tables have Row Level Security enforcing project membership via `shared_project_members`.\n- **Deep links**: `todoozy://invite/{token}` registered via `app.setAsDefaultProtocolClient()` with `open-url` handler on macOS.\n\n### Files created\n- `supabase/migrations/20260401000000_shared_projects.sql` — Supabase schema + RLS policies\n- `src/main/repositories/NotificationRepository.ts` — local notification CRUD\n- `src/main/repositories/SyncQueueRepository.ts` — offline sync queue\n- `src/renderer/src/services/SyncService.ts` — write-through, Realtime, invite management\n- `src/renderer/src/shared/stores/notificationStore.ts` — notification state\n- `src/renderer/src/shared/stores/syncStore.ts` — sync status state\n- `src/renderer/src/features/collaboration/` — MemberAvatars, InviteDialog, NotificationBell, NotificationPanel, MemberSettings, AssigneePicker\n- Test files for new repositories\n\n### Files modified\n- `src/shared/types.ts` — added collaboration types (Notification, SyncQueueEntry, SharedProjectInvite, etc.)\n- `src/main/database/migrations.ts` — migration 12: notifications, sync_queue, is_shared\n- `src/main/repositories/index.ts` — registered new repositories\n- `src/main/repositories/ProjectRepository.ts` — handle is_shared column\n- `src/main/ipc-handlers.ts` — notification and sync queue handlers\n- `src/main/index.ts` — todoozy:// protocol registration, deep link handling\n- `src/preload/index.ts` + `index.d.ts` — notifications, sync, invite APIs\n- `src/renderer/src/AppLayout.tsx` — share button, member avatars, notification bell\n- `src/renderer/src/App.tsx` — invite dialog flow\n- `src/renderer/src/features/sidebar/Sidebar.tsx` — shared project indicator icon\n- `src/renderer/src/features/settings/UnifiedSettingsModal.tsx` — Members tab\n\n### Test results\n- 372/372 tests passing (15 new tests for NotificationRepository and SyncQueueRepository)\n- npm run typecheck: zero errors"
